# Homepage absolute lock (owner-locked 2026-07-15)

**Priority:** Overrides all other agent impulses (refactors, fixes, polish, "while I'm here").

## Hard stop

Unless the project owner **explicitly names a homepage change in the current conversation**, you **MUST NOT** read, edit, create, delete, rename, or reformat any file in the homepage stack.

**Do not touch the homepage to fix unrelated tasks.** If a bug might involve homepage code, **stop and ask the owner first**.

## Frozen stack (every path)

- `app/page.tsx`
- `app/globals.css` (marketing / hero / landing utilities only — if unsure, do not edit)
- `components/marketing/**`
- `components/language-switcher.tsx`
- `lib/marketing/**`
- `lib/studioos/home-hero-space-asset.ts`
- `lib/studioos/marketing-headline-font.ts`
- `public/images/home-hero-space.png` and homepage hero / brand assets under `public/images/`
- Hero video resolver + proxy: `lib/marketing/home-hero-video-sources.ts`, `lib/marketing/marketing-video-proxy.ts`, `app/videos/[...path]/route.ts`

Canonical docs: [`docs/HOMEPAGE_GOLDEN.md`](../../docs/HOMEPAGE_GOLDEN.md) · [`components/marketing/README.md`](../../components/marketing/README.md)

## Forbidden without owner command

- Copy, spacing, fonts, colors, animations
- Mobile / iPad / desktop layout or breakpoints
- Hero background size/position, subtitle/title/CTA sizing
- Brand bar, marquee logos, hero-to-video spacing
- `HomeHeroVideo` player, video URLs, cache version `cv=7`
- Section order in `HomeLandingPage`
- Nav, footer, language switcher on homepage
- "Restore", "sync with production", "match vincis.app" unless owner asked **in this chat**

## Allowed without homepage command

- Changes **outside** the paths above (admin, API, portal, DB, etc.)
- Reading homepage files **only** to answer a question (no edits)

## Owner override (only valid key)

Owner must say **in the current conversation** what to change, e.g. "把手机 hero 副标题再放大" — change **only that**, nothing else.

## If you already changed homepage by mistake

Tell the owner immediately. Restore:

```bash
npm run homepage:restore:golden
# or
git checkout homepage-golden -- app/page.tsx components/marketing/ lib/marketing/ app/globals.css components/language-switcher.tsx
```

Verify lock: `npm run homepage:verify-lock`
